{"tid":959931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"真心呼籲大家食M記唔好自己收盤","createTime":"2018-12-29T04:20:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-29T04:27:46.000Z","uid":77588,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"35255d2117e709e52ff115c8f0d69c534d5085ee","tid":959931,"uid":77588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T04:20:39.000Z","msg":"有冇留意到做m記收盤個啲員工係咩人？<br />\n其實都係啲身體行動唔方便、好大年紀，或者智力有少少問題既人<br />\n我唔敢講全部都係，但真係見過唔少<br />\n<br />\n如果個個都懶有手尾，係度盡嗰啲所謂「公民責任」，搞到個場咁乾淨冇野執，m記見到根本唔需要佢地，咁佢地遲早就比人炒9晒<br />\n<br />\n講真佢地呢班人，好難再搵到工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以香港人，唔好好心做壞事"},{"pid":"e0c109ced414dc1adc4b8d5b8906f746a3a217a9","tid":959931,"uid":77588,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T04:22:01.000Z","msg":"仲有啊！m記一刀切走飲筒我屌你老母啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31842c15c337dcf61fd40fb762db2162079848cf","tid":959931,"uid":81256,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T04:27:46.000Z","msg":"其實員工最憎顧客自己執盤"}]}